Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样…不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有恋爱经验的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于这种事情一直很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是这样的我 当看到她流下眼泪之时也发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫到底是在和什么做斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么问我那种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会想说那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:36.52,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,水魔导师的攻击变强大了 请求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有她哭泣的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新发现 现在准备开始探索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有带伞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为樟叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会和樟叶扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体都变凉了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗住民的体温本来就是这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了点菜粥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\pos(608,318)\3c&H000000&\fs29}Episode XI 苍月下的…最终决战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\pos(664,288)\3c&H000000&\fs21}Blue moon·Ragnarok
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微坐起来一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实世界出现了歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为邪王真眼的力量也在减弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来烧还是没退下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也给我乖乖在家睡觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊 都已经感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天还勉强自己想到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就觉得头晕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(451,438)\fs21}Vanishiment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了一晚已经得到完全恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 直到病好为止都不准你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你到底是想去哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我不能回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前应该也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以闇炎之主的身份提问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底打算去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问完之后也不打算责怪你什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:03:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是很讨厌这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花对我有所隐瞒而去其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相很快就会昭然于天下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 为什么要撇下凸守我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成这幅样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,de…death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还没有死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会好了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你那么介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我随时都可以依靠邪王真眼的力量恢复健康
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道必须要服下盛开于邪王崖暗黑壁之巅的黑龙花才能痊愈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随意添加设定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你站得那么近小心被传染啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.02,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守我一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是待得太久也有被传染的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 奇美拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快点恢复哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作业堆了很多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚说出了禁言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了作业会皱眉头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 索菲娅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好几次想通过电子音信识别信号与她联络
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却从来没得到她的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 到底怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙好像说她很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很容易就能看出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫说了要开始战争的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就猜到大概就会发展到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么丹谷生你是发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一眼就发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子眼里就只有你一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是十花姐告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这之后你打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能对那个孩子坐视不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那么喜欢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你突然这么跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道该怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她甚至也从来没有跟我说过那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么突然变得这么正经了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生应该比较更了解恋爱这回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在回避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有刻意回避哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就别插手这件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花那个时候也是 总是发生什么立刻就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是因为看富樫你们很烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才来帮助你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没记得有拜托过你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香学姐 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么的话你不要把人撞倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么但是什么都有！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.59,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,你是凸守吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在做什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:06:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功归来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心你就死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要战胜内在的自己 就需要波纹和魔法能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这么轻易赞同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏这个这次我也成功打败敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得了最终胜利哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后 我就是魔法魔王少女改+α外传了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么有种续篇继续烂牌游戏的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此以前的事以后已经全部被我遗弃到了无知的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,统统消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫 这样真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天使的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会把她刚才的话当真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着「太好了 好像她没事」之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能 她只是在逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事怎么可能看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和七宫的交情也不是这一两天的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…你要我到底怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俗话说恋情如梦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是梦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着时间的流逝应该会慢慢地醒过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要强行叫醒她的话 反而会让她觉得痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 这不关你事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实小森大人她最喜欢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢小六花 小凸守还有富樫同学 小七宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她最喜欢中二病了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都觉得羡慕她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是中二病就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐你那么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 我就能和大家分享同一种感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也不是那么容易就能变成中二病的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你开始憧憬的那一刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是一名堂堂正正的中二病了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香学姐你不是第二代邪王真眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲亚 你好像处于迷茫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你已经取回你的记忆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要吃药草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想着这样比较容易对你传达我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才特地换衣服过来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这裙子可是很紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有箴言相赠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是魔法师 森夏的箴言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(457,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森夏以前曾与冒名之人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(275,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且对他们降下了惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何面对自己体内的另一个自己并与之对战的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个…自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 为了了解自己 应该将目光转向外面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我经由与冒牌货的对战 得以了解自己一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲亚你也有不得不战的对手才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请去寻找那个对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 你的前途将会一片光明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻烦啊 你懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 我帮你补充魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好近啊 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷霆战锤使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mjolnir Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不仅对闇炎之主出手 还把魔爪伸向了冒牌森大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樟叶 月亮出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是漂亮的满月哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说今晚是苍月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍蓝…之月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫喜欢我 但是我对六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂 太复杂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闇炎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要看看我的魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我寻找了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的对手果然只有勇者你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能这样做一个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是战争！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔王认证
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 六花不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才稍微不注意她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚有苍月对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 她已经注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是苍蓝之月的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍蓝之月？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的记不得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗炎龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者你曾经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡在自己体内的暗炎龙又会苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也希望它能被人唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自几经风霜的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来永恒不变的绝对契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使超越时间 超越次元 前往平行世界的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也意欲继续契约
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以其绝对的力量出现在我面前的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾错误地降生到这个混沌不堪的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因其强大的封印之力以及其篡改记忆的尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己真正的记忆正在逐渐被剥夺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾恐怕在不久的将来会化归虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以吾托付给汝 遥远的汝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将寄宿我体内的暗炎龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它的身姿在这个世界现身的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬 改变 重铸这个错误的世界的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活暗炎龙的钥匙有三个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯库尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薇儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:52.60,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}注：北欧神话中的诺恩三女神，是北欧神话中的命运女神。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我绝对的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有着与我共命运的力量之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集这三个钥匙应该不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之永远契约者啊 我将会等待那个时刻的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时步入沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在终将到来的苍蓝之月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能将那力量交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是…隐藏的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然记得不太清楚 大概就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…有人挖的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是邪王真眼放在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是找过这里的标记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也找过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都找不到兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是送往过去的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了将钥匙送往过去 只能使用平行世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张笔记里提到的平行世界的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在第十四个铁塔所指向的阴影之下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不知道那是从哪里开始数的第十四个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找到那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就这样一点一滴地彻查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「真相很快就会昭然于天下」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…一直为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模模糊糊地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近的风景我有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 无论何时都那么认真地去中二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时都那么认真地去恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在为我着想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花 六花 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太 这个就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兀儿德？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明感冒了 还来找这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是恶化了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为必须由绝对的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的契约者来唤醒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是勇太的永远的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 必须找出来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出来 将它作为证明…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事不用做也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是契约者 却连一把钥匙都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是索菲亚却…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太是我的契约者？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是你绝对的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在国中二年级的时候骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把它塞进那时的石膏里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的我 居然还做了这么麻烦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.93,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,水与柱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已的话 谁都看不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在金属上面刻字很麻烦 所以中途就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是很多年前放在这儿的东西 居然还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是块石头而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是唤醒暗炎龙的魔石…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍蓝之月…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我查过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就是苍月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 拜托你了 邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远的契约者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂吧 现实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绽开吧 神经突触
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vanishment this world！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 格尔松尼盎斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(441,438)\fs21}Ghelzonianses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是战争 让我与你的暗炎龙一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的全力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应当与之一战的对手 不可不战的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是与勇者齐思 共求 同弃的暗炎龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我不可不战的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我必须决出胜负的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是格尔松尼盎斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(451,438)\fs21}Ghelzonianses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏并重铸世界一切的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法魔王少女 期望未来永恒获得魔法的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让吾之暗炎龙的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深深地烙印进你的双目中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如我所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗炎龙根本不可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然更不可能被看见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后 六花的感冒复发倒床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太 我要回溯时空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让现在变成7月8日…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背负着崩溃状态的作业 迎来了暑假的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:20:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作业写不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦叶长大了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦叶也要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 我还是一次都没去过她们希望我过去的雅加达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的作业没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于新生的索菲亚来说这不是什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫在结束了与暗炎龙的战斗之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了向新的七宫的进化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 到底什么地方改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会变的 未来永远我都是魔法魔王少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以吾以不变之名 将郁集的东西破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保持不变从而需要参加使自己变得强大的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是连关定则吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 那就是连关定则哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你也要找天使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
